{"word":"G4785 - συγκαταψηφίζω - synkatapsēphízō - soong-kat-aps-ay-fid'-zo - Number with","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκαταψηφίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synkatapsēphízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soong-kat-aps-ay-fid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Number with</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சேர்த்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to assign one a place among (sun), to vote one a place among"},{"paragraph":"2. to vote against with others,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and a compound of <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G5585 - ψηφίζω - psēphízō - psay-fid'-zo/5585\">G5585</a>; to <i>count down</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, <i>enroll among:</i> - number with.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4785/4785\">G4785</a>, <a href=\"#/G4860/4860\">G4860</a>, <a href=\"#/G5585/5585\">G5585</a>, <a href=\"#/G5586/5586\">G5586</a>"}]}